org.gitlab.api

Class Pagination

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gitlab.api.Pagination

  • public final class Pagination
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the class that represents a pagination with page number and page size. Gitlab Web API: https://docs.gitlab.com/ee/api/#pagination
